title: Best of The Herd for 12/23/2019
itunes:title: Best of The Herd for 12/23/2019
description:
Colin laughs at people complaining about what Dak Prescott didn't have when you compare it to what Carson Wentz is working with. He says Sam Darnold and Baker Mayfield are remarkably similar but one fan base is already sick of their QB because of his attitude. He calls the Cowboys a mentally and physically soft team and talks about it with Cowboys Insider Matt Mosley. Plus, Colin admits where he was right and wrong over the weekend.
